a record-setting baby boom!

209
00:12:43,166 --> 00:12:44,083
[TAKUMI]
Oh, crap!

210
00:12:44,166 --> 00:12:46,166
This has never happened before!

211
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:49,083
It's not an EMP, and it's
not a virus either, yeah!

212
00:12:49,166 --> 00:12:51,083
